<<<
1 John 4:19

We love whom? Psalm 9:1-2 where David says "I will give thanks to the LORD with all my heart; I will tell of all Your wonders."

Matthew 12:34 - "You brood of vipers! How can you speak good, when you are evil? For out of the abundance of the heart the mouth speaks."

Everything that we do is out of desire to glorify God.

David's desire to love others came from His desire to love God. David's desire to love God came from God's decision to love David.

