!! Takeaways
* The reason our love of God must precede our love of others therefore, is because the former derives the latter. Therefore if we are struggling to develop a heart for the lost, we must first develop a heart for God.

* Our love of God is entirely preceded by our being loved of God. Therefore if we are struggling to develop a heart for God, we must ask of God!

* The reason our love of God must precede our love of others therefore, is because the former drives the latter.
